1. On je imao jednu *ćerku* (He had one daughter).
2. *Ćerka* je otišla u školu (The daughter went to school).
3. Ona je imala dve *ćerke* (She had two daughters).
4. *Ćerka* je bila puno radoznala (The daughter was very curious).
5. Ona ima tri *ćerke* (She has three daughters).
6. *Ćerka* je bila jako ljubazna (The daughter was very kind).
7. Oni su posetili *ćerku* (They visited the daughter).
8. *Ćerka* je bila ponosna na njega (The daughter was proud of him).